slides.title: VMD15 facebookpage network
slides.text: This is the network seen from a distance. This view both includes, comments, photos, videos and link.

slides.title: Close up
slides.text: This view shows both the comments, videos, links and photos. The red nodes are the comments and as you can see the users in this network seem to use comments a lot more than the other options they have.

slides.title: Selective view
slides.text: The green nodes are the photos. This view shows how the other nodes than comments are all big nodes, but there are a lot less of them. The spreading of the photos, links and videos are big and they do not seem to cluster up based on the type of post.
